The paper discusses machine learning algorithms and their categorization based on the degree of supervision. This topic falls under the broad category of machine learning, which is covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. However, given the focus on learning algorithms and their supervision, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
